<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10525610>
    dc:description "Figs 1-5. Figs 1, 2, Acanthomerosternoplon paradoxum Tippmann, 1955: 1, dorsal habitus; 2, tarsal claw. Figs 3-5, tarsal claw: 3, Scopadus ciliatus Pascoe, 1857; 4, Cyrtinus pygmaeus (Haldeman, 1847); 5, Cyrtinus meridialis Martins & Galileo 2010." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10525610/files/figure.png" ;
